Three Logins:-
-Job Seekers
-Admin 
-Business House/ Companies

Job Seekers:-
-Should fill Form for sign up and create CV according to entered data.
-After filling form , Email verification code will be sent 
and verify entering to that code.
-After verification , Auto redirect to payment option and there will be Qr code and Screenshot attach place.
-After making payment Screenshot will be uploaded there and sends to admin.
-After admin verifying payment he/she can apply to jobs. He/she will not be able to see company name and details for can see Job vacancy and apply to it.

Admin;-
-After job seeker fills the form , and make payment . Admin verify that taking referense as Screenshot of payment.
-Admin can create company profiles , and also update the details of Job seekers.
-Admin can add job categories.
-Post and update Jobs.
-Auto delete account after 10-15 days if job seekers doesn't pay.

Business  House:-
-Sign up and submitted company documents for approval.
-Can post /edit /update and delete job .
-will not be able to see job seeker contact no , name and email . Can only see experience and skills.
-Should approve/reject job seekers application based on experience and skills.

